  23,23,"Yaha! Achiika! Ti (Tinim‚Äô Naawuni) daa tim Annabi Nuhu n-zaŇč chaŇč o niriba sani, ka o ti yőĶli: ‚ÄúYaa yinim‚Äô n niriba! JőĶmmi ya Naawuni, yi ka Duuma so na…£ila Ňäuna. Dini b…ĒŇč…Ē, yi ku zo Naawuni?‚ÄĚ"
  23,24,"Ka asanzanim‚Äô ban niŇč ch…õfuritali o niriba puuni yőĶli: ‚ÄúŇäumb…ĒŇč…Ē pala so na…£ila ninsala yi tatabo, ka o b…Ēriniotibgio maŇč‚Äô yi zu…£u. Yaha! Naawuni yi di b…Ēra, o naan si…£isi Malaaikanim‚Äô na, tinim‚Äô na  íin wum Ňč…Ē maa ti banim‚Äô ban pun gari maa ( í…õmana) puuni.‚ÄĚ"
  23,25,"O pala so m-pahila ninvu…£u so Ňčun kpe yinyőĶri. Dinzu…£u,  íinimi ya n-guhi o hali ni saha b…õla."
